<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1939-09-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1939-09-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="716" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d716">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">811.04418/553a</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName>
                                to the British Prime Minister</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Chamberlain</hi></persName>)<note n="21" xml:id="d716fn21">Photostatic copy obtained from the Franklin D.
                                Roosevelt Library, Hyde Park, N. Y.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-09-11">September 11, 1939</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Chamberlain</hi>: I need not tell you
                            that you have been much in my thoughts during these difficult days and
                            further that I hope you will at all times feel free to write me
                            personally and outside of diplomatic procedure about any problems as
                            they arise.</p>
                        <p>I hope and believe that we shall repeal the embargo within the next month
                            and this is definitely a part of the Administration policy.</p>
                        <p>With my sincere regards</p>
                        <p>Faithfully yours,</p>
                        <closer>[<signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Franklin D. Roosevelt</hi>
                            </signed>]</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>